      "cooked": "<p>Hi hoping someone can help!</p>\n<p>When using ERG I\u2019m getting some issues reaching target watts and keeping there, it also keeps dropping down. I\u2019ve added some links to the file so you can see the issue.</p>\n<p>I have added my most recent ride here - <a href=\"https://app.trainerday.com/activities/64670e5a8f00008ec6e1f518\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Trainer Day</a></p>\n<p>I have added the Test ERG ride here - <a href=\"https://app.trainerday.com/activities/646712658f00008ec6e1fa7b\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Trainer Day</a></p>\n<p>Hopefully the links work!</p>\n<p>Smart Trainer - Saris H3<br>\nWahoo Cadence Sensor<br>\nWahoo HR Chest Strap<br>\nDevice - Google 7 Pro</p>\n<p>Many thanks!</p>",
