      "created_at": "2023-05-23T21:36:46.413Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Strange you posted that as I have the same issue with the flight trainer from 4iiii. I started to use higher watts and although I spin at more than 100 rpm, I cannot reach 400 watts for example. I am currently working with support to see if it is an app issue or a  trainer limitation. Until now, I never went above 300 watts so I had no trouble. I will update th\u00e9 thread when I get more data</p>",
