      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/e19adc/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2023-05-30T20:16:12.940Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I have been asking 4iiii support to tell me on how to use their app to see if the power not reaching the target in high watts is an app or trainer issue. for 2 weeks they have been sending me articles on how to setup and configure the trainer. Like i have been using it for 3 years now. So no help there. i downgraded the firmware and now everything works fine. I reach the target and higher. So trainer day app is working fine. I am going to test it with my ant+ tacx dongle to see on how it behaves as yesterday when i was doing sprint, it seems like the connected was cut in Bluetooth and i was spinning easy. stopping and restarting worked.</p>",
